code[class*="language-"], pre[class*="language-"] { color: black; background: none; text-shadow: white 0px 1px; font-family: Consolas, Monaco, "Andale Mono", "Ubuntu Mono", monospace; text-align: left; white-space: pre; word-spacing: normal; word-break: normal; overflow-wrap: normal; line-height: 1.5; tab-size: 4; hyphens: none; }

pre[class*="language-"]::selection, pre[class*="language-"] ::selection, code[class*="language-"]::selection, code[class*="language-"] ::selection { text-shadow: none; background: rgb(179, 212, 252); }
pre.line-numbers { position: relative; padding-left: 3.8em; counter-reset: linenumber 0; }

.line-numbers .line-numbers-rows { position: absolute; pointer-events: none; top: 0px; font-size: 100%; left: -3.8em; width: 3em; letter-spacing: -1px; border-right: 1px solid rgb(153, 153, 153); user-select: none; }
.line-numbers-rows > span { pointer-events: none; display: block; counter-increment: linenumber 1; }
.line-numbers-rows > span::before { content: counter(linenumber); color: rgb(153, 153, 153); display: block; padding-right: 0.8em; text-align: right; }
.tooltip { border-bottom: 1px dotted rgb(0, 120, 215); color: rgb(0, 120, 215); cursor: help; }
.baloon { position: absolute; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; display: none; }

.inner-box { margin: 0px; padding: 5px 10px; border-left: 1px solid rgb(150, 150, 150); border-right: 1px solid rgb(150, 150, 150); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 10pt; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.25em; }
.r1, .r2, .r3, .r4 { display: block; height: 1px; overflow: hidden; font-size: 1px; }
.baloon .r3, .baloon .r2, .baloon .r1 { border-left: 1px solid rgb(150, 150, 150); border-right: 1px solid rgb(150, 150, 150); }
ul { list-style: square; padding-left: 35px; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.25; }
h2, h2 a, h2 a:hover { font-size: 20pt; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(0, 120, 215); text-decoration: none; margin-bottom: 25px; }
h3, h3 a, h3 a:hover { font-size: 16pt; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); text-decoration: none; margin-top: 45px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
h4, h4 a, h4 a:hover { font-size: 12pt; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); text-decoration: none; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 0px; }
div.bs-content ol ol a { color: rgb(50, 50, 50); }
div.bs-content ol { list-style-type: none; counter-reset: item 0; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; }
div.bs-content li { display: table; counter-increment: item 1; }
div.bs-content li::before { content: counters(item, ".") ". "; display: table-cell; padding-right: 10px; }
div.bs-card { border: 1px solid rgb(200, 200, 200); padding: 15px; line-height: 1.5; }
div.bs-card div.attr { width: 85px; padding-right: 15px; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); display: table-cell; }
div.bs-card div.value { color: rgb(50, 50, 50); display: table-cell; }
div.bs-var > div { padding: 5px 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(225, 225, 225); }
div.bs-var div.number { font-family: Consolas, Monaco, "Andale Mono", "Ubuntu Mono", monospace; width: 25px; padding-right: 15px; display: table-cell; color: rgb(150, 150, 150); text-align: right; }
div.bs-var div.name { font-family: Consolas, Monaco, "Andale Mono", "Ubuntu Mono", monospace; width: 110px; padding-right: 15px; display: table-cell; color: rgb(192, 22, 33); }
div.bs-var div.value { font-family: Consolas, Monaco, "Andale Mono", "Ubuntu Mono", monospace; width: 160px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 0px; display: table-cell; color: rgb(49, 141, 0); }
div.bs-var div.desc { display: table-cell; color: rgb(50, 50, 50); }

span.bs-var { font-family: Consolas, Monaco, "Andale Mono", "Ubuntu Mono", monospace; color: rgb(0, 120, 215); background-color: rgb(242, 239, 236); padding: 3px 4px 1px; margin-left: 1px; margin-right: 1px; }
p.bs-comment { padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(0, 143, 212); background-color: rgb(238, 249, 254); }
p.bs-note { padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(255, 203, 5); background-color: rgb(255, 252, 213); }
p.bs-attention { padding: 15px; margin-bottom: 25px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(237, 28, 36); background-color: rgb(255, 241, 235); }
div.bs-table { margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 25px; display: table; border-collapse: collapse; }

div.bs-table > div > div { display: table-cell; padding: 5px 15px; color: rgb(100, 100, 100); }

rulesList.cssText: img.wp-smiley, img.emoji { display: inline !important; border: none !important; box-shadow: none !important; height: 1em !important; width: 1em !important; margin: 0px 0.07em !important; vertical-align: -0.1em !important; background: none !important; padding: 0px !important; }
.screen-reader-text { border: 0px; clip-path: inset(50%); height: 1px; margin: -1px; overflow: hidden; padding: 0px; position: absolute; width: 1px; overflow-wrap: normal !important; }

.screen-reader-text:focus { background-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); clip-path: none; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); display: block; font-size: 1em; height: auto; left: 5px; line-height: normal; padding: 15px 23px 14px; text-decoration: none; top: 5px; width: auto; z-index: 100000; }

.wp-block-button__link { color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(50, 55, 60); border-radius: 9999px; box-shadow: none; text-decoration: none; padding: calc(0.667em + 2px) calc(1.333em + 2px); font-size: 1.125em; }
.wp-block-file__button { background: rgb(50, 55, 60); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: none; }
